column5: A small town doctor was famous in the area for always catching VERY large fish.  One day while he was on one of his frequent fishing trips, he got a call that a woman at a neighboring farm was giving birth.  He rushed to her aid and delivered a healthy baby boy.  The farmer had nothing to weigh the baby with so the doctor used his fishing scale.  The baby weighed in at 32 pounds, 10 ounces!
I think Skeeter Dann has the same scale! - lol
well Tracker, if you could EVER catch a fish then we could weigh it to find out!!! ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~`  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
